sequenceDiagram
    actor Approver

    participant Review as Review Pengajuan
    participant System
    participant DB as Database
    participant PDF as PDF Generator

    Approver->>Review: buka menu review pengajuan
    Review->>System: request daftar pengajuan

    System->>DB: ambil data pengajuan pending
    DB-->>System: data pengajuan
    System-->>Review: tampil daftar pengajuan

    Approver->>Review: pilih pengajuan
    Review->>System: request detail pengajuan

    System->>DB: ambil detail pengajuan
    DB-->>System: detail + dokumen
    System-->>Review: tampil detail pengajuan

    Approver->>Review: pilih Setuju / Tolak
    Review->>System: kirim keputusan

    alt Approver memilih Setuju

        System->>DB: simpan persetujuan

        alt Approver terakhir
            System->>DB: ubah status Hard-Lock
            System->>PDF: generate surat izin + QR
            PDF-->>System: file PDF
            System-->>Review: status berhasil disetujui
        else Masih ada approver berikutnya
            System->>DB: teruskan ke approver berikutnya
            System-->>Review: pengajuan diteruskan
        end

    else Approver memilih Tolak

        System-->>Review: minta alasan penolakan
        Approver->>Review: isi alasan penolakan
        Review->>System: kirim alasan

        alt alasan diisi
            System->>DB: simpan penolakan
            System-->>Review: pengajuan ditolak
        else alasan kosong
            System-->>Review: tampil pesan error
        end

    end

    Review-->>Approver: tampil halaman review